      * @deny (create) User from a different tenant.
      * @allow (get, list) Authenticated user within the tenant.
      * @deny (get, list) User from a different tenant.
      * @allow (update, delete) Authenticated user within the tenant.
      * @deny (update, delete) User from a different tenant.
